                <div class="text-4xl mb-4 text-center">
                    <span role="img" aria-label="Leader Icon">🧭</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 text-center">리더십 유형 테스트</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm text-center">
